name: Ledet Training Public GitHub Pages
body:
### Welcome to The Ledet GitHub Pages.
Ledet Training is an Adobe, Autodesk and Authorized Training company headquartered in Atlanta, GA with additional offices in Chicago, Denver, Houston, San Diego and Washington DC. This GitHub repository provides resources for developers, contractors, instructors, and partners.

### Authors and Contributors
@sjledet - Sterling Ledet
